TestArrayRootReadFileNavigatesFirstElement
/ read file.json whose root is an array — %content[0].name% resolves; the
/ implicit-first trick %content.name% also resolves to content[0].name when no
/ list-intrinsic key matches.
- set %people% = [{name:"alice"}, {name:"bob"}]
- write %people% to file %arrFile%
- read file %arrFile%, write to %content%
- assert %content[0].name% equals "alice"
- assert %content.name% equals "alice"
- delete file %arrFile%
